### Create new product
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
    "name": "Product2",
    "description": "Description of product 2",
    "price": 10,
    "quantity": 100
}


### Get All products
GET {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### Get Product by Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


